{"tid":351405,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心跌入設計陷阱！明思設計集團有限公司","createTime":"2017-08-08T04:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T04:24:47.000Z","uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a90101b7f545991bb883832f2bd93523f00b85d","tid":351405,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/am730hk/videos/1497189426986806/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fam730hk%2Fvideos%2F1497189426986806%2F&d=wf4GiX5tyj8uccFk1MzqeMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=5994df23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/am730hk/videos/1497189426986806/</a><br />\n<br />\n【長片慎入 你是苦主嗎?】一間裝修公司向客戶由最初報價17萬元後暴增至79萬裝修費，被海關檢控，並首次引用《商品說明條例》成功入罪，判刑雖不重，但案件激發大眾熱議。原因是不少經歷過裝修的市民，都曾遇過不快，區議會以至消委會頻頻接投訴，打官司更不計其數。誤墮裝修陷阱，不僅想安居樂業的美夢無法即時實現，有人甚至從此墮入惡夢。本報追訪3位曾誤墮裝修陷阱的受害人訴說經歷，包括全屋漏電漏水，甚至無辜被收數公司上門追數。消委會及測量師學會亦警告，消費者一旦怕煩怕面懵，就是最易跌入裝修陷阱的第一步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/121422_65aba9411d88bc86d22d9504fce4ac21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F121422_65aba9411d88bc86d22d9504fce4ac21.jpg&h=31b7d012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba7f31677f686d56fb235d9392f2513c5f3c14e5","tid":351405,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"一年呃過千萬 罰就罰3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d350d50af310a78038181e8209ae50c472c4b1a9","tid":351405,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"880bd5cf51815eea6de6fc17cd4e17a593655c76","tid":351405,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"鼓勵人犯罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  說好的商品說明條例？"},{"pid":"d12b0f